name: offset
doc: voltage offset, range depends on amplitude

name: phase
doc: phase with respect to sync and rear-panel connectors

name: load
doc: output load (50 Ohm or High-Z). Ohms or 'MIN', 'MAX'

name: pulse_hold
doc: maintains/holds the pulse width or the pulse duty-cycle

name: pulse_transition
doc: edge time in seconds (both rising and falling)

name: event_status_enable
doc: enable bits in the event status register

name: clear_status
doc: clear the event register in all register groups

name: power_on_clear
doc: clear the standard event enable register

name: set_opc
doc: Set the operation complete bit in the standard event register
